::DarkMouse::
She sat up on the table and looked at Scorponok. Her optics glowed bright 
red.  She new who was in command and 2nd in command.  She knew who's orders 
to obey and to follow them out without hesitation.
"Internal diagnostic, fully functional. Awaiting orders."

She snapped out of it and shook her head."WHoah, what a rush.  You should 
try that sometime yourself Scorponok."
